<li><span class="ILHItem"><span class="ILHChinese"><a href="/w/index.php?title=%E5%85%8B%E9%87%8C%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E6%B5%B7%E5%A7%86%E6%96%AF%E6%B2%83%E6%96%AF&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="克里斯·海姆斯沃斯（尚未撰写）">克里斯·海姆斯沃斯</a></span><span class="ILHComment" style="display:none;">（<span style="font-size:smaller;"><span class="ILHLang">英语</span>：</span><span class="ILHOriginal" lang="en" style="font-size:smaller;" xml:lang="en">-{<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chris_Hemsworth" class="extiw" title="en:Chris Hemsworth">Chris Hemsworth</a>}-</span>）</span></span>饰<span class="ILHItem"><span class="ILHChinese"><a href="/w/index.php?title=%E8%80%81%E4%B9%94%E6%B2%BB%C2%B7%E5%A1%9E%E7%BC%AA%E5%B0%94%C2%B7%E6%9F%AF%E5%85%8B&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="老乔治·塞缪尔·柯克（尚未撰写）">老乔治·塞缪尔·柯克</a></span><span class="ILHComment" style="display:none;">（<span style="font-size:smaller;"><span class="ILHLang">英语</span>：</span><span class="ILHOriginal" lang="en" style="font-size:smaller;" xml:lang="en">-{<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Samuel_Kirk,_Sr." class="extiw" title="en:George Samuel Kirk, Sr.">George Samuel Kirk, Sr.</a>}-</span>）</span></span>，柯克之父，在联邦星舰开尔文号与罗慕伦人战斗时战死。</li>

